 Business Process Analyst 

Help a leading organisation design process for support of AV/VC across multiple sites 

Alchemy Recruitment Consulting is partnered with a leading resources company in their search for a Business Analyst to join their technology team based in Brisbane CBD. This company promotes flexible working and offers an exceptional work culture. This position is offered on an initial 3-month contract. 

 About the role: 
The role is responsible for converting user and business processes, information and needs to identify and outline methods for process transformation. In this role as Business Analyst you will be tasked with: 
 Designing & developing the process for sites located across Queensland to engage resources to manage & support VC / AV; 
 Engaging with stakeholders in order to understand and obtain requirements and translate business requirements into specifications; 
 Analysis, design and specification of new and existing systems to support the business using appropriate standards, methodologies and toolsets. 

 Skills required: 
 Strong business analysis skills and experience in detailed analysis and understanding of the functional requirements and business process documentation, including the tracking of functional and process changes; 
 Consulting and negotiating with diverse stakeholders and driving outcomes within acceptable costs and timelines; 
 Distilling business needs to identify fit for purpose options; 
