 Proven experience in the application of technology solutions to business problems in large organisations, providing scoping and implementation services; 
 Demonstrated experience in providing innovative solutions and initiating action when problems arise; 
 Excellent verbal and written communication skills; 
 Ability to analyse business requirements and needs, converting them into a technical solution; 
 Ability to work within specifications and to timeframes. 

 Culture 

At illion, we are always seeking innovative and forward-thinking individuals to join us on our journey. Our culture is unique. It's fast, results-driven and dynamic. It's certainly not for everyone. But if you thrive in a high performing environment - illion could be for you! 

Benefits 

